<% content_for :message do %>
  <p>
    Hi!
  </p>

  <p>
    We're working hard to reply to everyone, and we'll respond to you as soon as we can. Your communication is greatly
    valued, and it will be reviewed and answered by our volunteer Support team. In the meantime, here is a copy of the
    information you submitted through the Technical Support and Feedback form:
  </p>
  
  <%= style_quote("<b>" + (raw @summary) + "</b>" + (raw @comment)) %>

  <p>If you have additional questions or information, do not hesitate to send in another ticket.</p>

  <p>
    Regards,<br/>
    the AO3 Support team
  </p>
<% end %>

<% content_for :sent_at do %>
  <%= Time.now.to_s(:time_for_mailers) %>
<% end %>
